bin/apply_brand <branddir> <branch>

generates a branded version of the source code
It grabs the source from the specified branch of a clone of the current repository, as reported by git config --get remote.origin.url

Call it from working directory us 
<brandir> shall be absolute pathname. relative pathnames could produce undefined behaviour.
<branch> git branch 

After execution, directory brand_<brandname> contains the new patched codebase


